Project description

winrt-Windows.Devices.Bluetooth.Rfcomm

Windows Runtime (WinRT) APIs for for the Windows.Devices.Bluetooth.Rfcomm namespace.

This package provides the winrt.windows.devices.bluetooth.rfcomm module.
